## Standard Error Wrapper
- Use a consistent error-handling utility across services
- Include error codes, messages, and stack traces in logs

## No Silent Failures
- Never swallow errors silently
- Always log unexpected errors

## Retry Logic
- Use exponential backoff for retryable errors (e.g., rate limits)

## Input Validation
- Validate request payloads before processing
- Reject invalid inputs early
